.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, animation, spy, western, superhero
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, dancing, baking, skydiving, cooking
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
City: boston, hamburg, edinburgh, nizza, venice
1. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes red
2. the person watching swedish movies is the person traveling to edinburgh
3. the person watching animation movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person who's hobby is dancing
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person traveling to hamburg
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle
9. the person watching western movies is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston
11. the person traveling to venices is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's hobby is camping
13. the person watching spy movies is the prince-smoker
14. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Movie-Genre	|   western	|    animation	|    horror	|    spy	|    swedish	|
| City		|     boston	|    venice	|     hamburg	|     nizza	|      edinburgh	|
| Hobby	|    cooking	|     skydiving	|     baking	|    dancing	|      camping	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
